thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Adrian & Hua

author: Adrian & Hua
title: Adrian & Hua
text: Peter has helped us to sell our small apartment recently. He was very patient and worked hard till selling our property successfully. It was a hard campaign and stressed me at one stage. Thankfully Peter kept on working hard, regardless this was just a small property. Really appreciate his help.
